Ingredients:

-Desi ghee (Clarified butter) 2 tbs

-Gond (Edible gum) ½ Cup (100g)

-Badam (Almonds) ½ Cup

-Pista (Pistachios) ½ Cup

-Akhrot (Walnuts) ½ Cup

-Kaju (Cashew nuts) ½ Cup

-Char maghaz (Melon seeds) ¼ Cup

-Phool makhanay (Lotus seeds) 2 Cups (50g)

-Desi ghee (Clarified butter) 1/3 Cup

-Doodh (Milk) 3 Cups (750ml)

-Desi gur (Organic jaggery) ½ Cup (100g)

-Khashkhash (Poppy seeds) ¼ Cup

-Sonth powder (Ginger powder) 2 tbs

-Elaichi powder (Cardamom powder) 1 tsp

-Jaifil powder (Nutmeg powder) ½ tsp

 

Directions:

In a wok,add clarified butter & let it melt.

-Add edible gum,mix well & fry on low flame until it puffs up.

-In a mortal & pestle,add fried edible gum,crush coarsely & set aside.
